Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- Teacher, what do you need?\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Sit down! Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, the other day...\NWhat was it, five minutes is critical?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,No, no.\N"Five minutes later, it ends unexpectedly."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it. I just want to see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that why you called me here?\NWhy don't you just watch it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, let me ask you something.\NHow can I see it with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.56,Main,,0,0,0,,A mobile phone? No way.\NYes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- Please, Generation Z.\N- Hey, don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.16,0:00:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,As expected of Generation Z.\NYou work fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Generation Z? Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:50.75,New,,0,0,0,,SURPRISE ENDING AFTER 5 MINUTES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:55.85,Main,,0,0,0,,LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:02.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- Are you nervous?\N- Yes... but being a motorcycle policemen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,is what I've been longing for it\Nsince I was little. I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:09.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine, as long\Nas you take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:11.92,Main,,0,0,0,,When it's over, let's have a debut party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:16.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be patrolling there.\NCall me if you find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:46.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop right there! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared, don't be scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't drive like that.\NIt's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:13.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- I wasn't driving that fast.\N- I saw you pass by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:16.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You were going over the\Nlegal speed limit of 30km/hr!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Please come outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- Please present your driver's license.\N- I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:33.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- I got a speeding ticket a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean you're\Ndriving without a license?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:40.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What a bad driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:42.39,Main,,0,0,0,,This car belongs to you, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course not!\NI can't drive this car!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- Whose car is it?\N- I don't know. I stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:57.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Speeding, driving without a license,\Nand theft! I'll take that as a "yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:03:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes he is a bad guy...\Nand he's totally unfazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:05.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I check the vehicle\Nregistration certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Then we can see who this car belongs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:13.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Vehicle registration? Yes, just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I may have seen it when\NI put my handgun away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.03,Main,,0,0,0,,A handgun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there a handgun in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:31.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no... This is too bad...\NThis guy's not just a bad man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:34.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's such a\Nserious case for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- Oh, I remember now.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:44.03,Main,,0,0,0,,The owner of this car is a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I killed her with that gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:52.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You... killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,He killed a woman, and he's just fine!\NThis is what you call a psychopath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:09.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Senpai! Excuse me.\NPlease back me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- What's wrong?\N- There's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:21.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:24.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way to dump the\Ndead body in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there a dead body on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:29.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's in the trunk right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's a dead body there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- Hey.\N- Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- What happened?\N- That... that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:25.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I stopped him from speeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,He said he didn't have his driver's\Nlicense and that he stole the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The gun was near the dashboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.30,Main,,0,0,0,,In the trunk, I'm told\Nthere's a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:39.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'll handle it here. You call for backup.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Take care. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:44.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- You never know what he might do.\N- Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Let us ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean you don't\Nhave a driver's license?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- I do have a driver's license.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- Doesn't sound fake to me.\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,This car is not stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:41.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I also have a vehicle\Nregistration certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,The dashboard, may I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,No handgun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hadgun? There is no way there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see the trunk, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:13.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What did he report to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That you were driving\Na stolen car with no
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.66,Main,,0,0,0,,license and you are in\Npossession of a handgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:23.26,Main,,0,0,0,,- He said you're carrying a dead body.\N- Dead body? There's no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.30,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:30.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That cop is a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe there are other lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I was speeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh~ I didn't expect this ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Teacher, you're an ex-drama club member.\NWhen a thing happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell\Na brilliant lie like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:07:59.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't act like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- You can do it.\N- I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- Then, let's go.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, wheeen, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:10.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- Sir, license out!\N- What? I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even going 10 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Please wait a minute.\NI'm sorry. This is a point card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:17.30,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my number card.\NThis is the fourth one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the fifth one.\NI'm sorry. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.49,Main,,0,0,0,,No, this is an insurance card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:26.13,Copy of New,,0,0,0,,SURPRISE MISTAKE ON THE FIFTH CARD
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:29.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that, teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:35.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Generation Z doesn't understand the\Ncarotid docking then dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Booooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.72,Main,,0,0,0,,THE GRIM REAPER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Your disease is stomach cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Stomach cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, of the skilful type.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:05.03,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the area that has been\Neroded by the cancer cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:08.63,Main,,0,0,0,,The cancer has metastasized deep\Ninto the lungs. It is now in stage 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,At this point,\Nsurgery will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:14.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. That means
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.30,Main,,0,0,0,,does that mean there's\Nnothing we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, so how much more do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.63,Main,,0,0,0,,If you do not receive\Nlife-prolonging treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:32.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it is unlikely that you will be\Nable to see the cherry blossoms next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:36.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I would like to explain about the\Nlife-prolonging treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,The main treatment is\Nchemotherapy or radiation therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Chemotherapy is\Nso-called anticancer drug therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a drug that\Nkills cancer cells but
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,it also attacks normal cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:20.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You haven't eaten at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:24.97,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Eat properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I still have some of\Nyesterday's sake left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You've been drinking too\Nmuch lately, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.97,Main,,0,0,0,,When you become a member of society,\Nyou have a lot of social life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, what\Ndid your physician said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, he said I have a little\Nmetabolic syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:45.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, they're going\Nto say that to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:50.49,Main,,0,0,0,,At your age?\NEat your vegetables, vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I said I can't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You should eat tomatoes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.46,Main,,0,0,0,,If no life-prolonging treatment is given,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I think the possibility of seeing\Ncherry blossoms next year is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:31.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.09,Main,,0,0,0,,DIR. WATANABE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of family\NShoichi is going to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to die without\Nseeing my grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:19.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Masami,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I said we'd travel to many places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.29,Main,,0,0,0,,MASAMI TAKAMURA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.33,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll figure it out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:07.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Daddy, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.97,Main,,0,0,0,,At the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:14.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You're absent today?\NI got a call from your manager, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:21.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Something strange happened\Nsince yesterday, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Masami...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:27.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- There was a call from the hospital.\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,There was a mistake,\Nthey want me to come over right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The one I showed you yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,is from another patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,To a man with the\Nsame last name,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like the x-ray\Ntechnician made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:54.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yours is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You have a little bit of\Ngastroptosis but no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:02.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So I don't have cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:05.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- What about next year's cherry blossoms?\N- You can see it without problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank God! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, It's bad, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea\NI've been through so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I am very sorry.
